{"tid":2113762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［娛樂圈群組］ 歌手麥德羅，女新人施匡翹確診 施匡翹每周要去新城做節目三日前與薛凱琪有親密合照","createTime":"2020-07-18T10:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T17:33:27.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"52fbbe5b1b8d86ec232e6795b3f84b7b0d75d689","tid":2113762,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"據悉麥德羅昨晚發現自「中招」，女友Apple姐昨晚即刻去做檢測，也發現被傳染，同時公司巡台宣傳人員阿Kai也是傳播鏈之一，女新人施匡翹每周曾跟Apple姐學唱歌，而施匡翹每周也到新城開咪做節目，所以他們這個感染群組牽涉好廣。阿Kai連日又不停帶藝人行台，另大家分別都有相約朋友約會。施匡翹的IG昨日貼出做GYM相，她說：「我們在這段時間一定會捱得過去。」施匡翹的IG三日前都貼出了跟薛凱琪見面的親密合照<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200718/6FMSTBHWTJ32N5YUMBZML4E6QQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200718%2F6FMSTBHWTJ32N5YUMBZML4E6QQ%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=c9d3def0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200718%2F6FMSTBHWTJ32N5YUMBZML4E6QQ%2F&h=49718e97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200718/6FMSTBHWTJ32N5YUMBZML4E6QQ/</a>"},{"pid":"2787b1e4efc9998a0c9ec3ebfc4c8866485b92d0","tid":2113762,"uid":216676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"邊位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aed34bacce24f94211bd62e7f43fe7f25cc7f1b","tid":2113762,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c57fdbb3ceb78d1711c877b2efe4f1f7bb61b9c0","tid":2113762,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"唔色"},{"pid":"fc95e9a8527ec7ec4a09a4d2981ae3a43ac6edea","tid":2113762,"uid":34047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:29:57.000Z","msg":"who到1001"},{"pid":"b7bb274303fb76cd45611268e782749c013480ee","tid":2113762,"uid"